# User Stories

## Overview

User stories describe the functionality of FlowDesk from the perspective of its users. They capture what each type of user wants to accomplish and the value the feature provides.

Each user story follows the format:

> **As a [user], I want to [action], so that [benefit].**

---

# Business Owner

## Account & Business

- As a business owner, I want to create an account so that I can access FlowDesk.
- As a business owner, I want to register my business so that I can start managing it online.
- As a business owner, I want to update my business profile so that my business information remains accurate.
- As a business owner, I want to upload my business logo so that my brand is displayed throughout the platform.
- As a business owner, I want to configure my business hours so that customers can only book available times.

---

## Dashboard

- As a business owner, I want to view a dashboard so that I can quickly understand how my business is performing.
- As a business owner, I want to view today's appointments so that I know what work is scheduled.
- As a business owner, I want to see customer and booking statistics so that I can monitor business growth.

---

## Staff Management

- As a business owner, I want to add employees so that they can access the platform.
- As a business owner, I want to edit employee information so that staff details remain up to date.
- As a business owner, I want to remove employees so that former staff no longer have access.
- As a business owner, I want to assign roles and permissions so that employees only access relevant features.

---

## Customer Management

- As a business owner, I want to add new customers so that I can maintain a customer database.
- As a business owner, I want to edit customer information so that records remain accurate.
- As a business owner, I want to search for customers so that I can quickly access their information.
- As a business owner, I want to view customer history so that I can provide better service.

---

## Services

- As a business owner, I want to create services so that customers can book them.
- As a business owner, I want to edit service details so that pricing and duration remain accurate.
- As a business owner, I want to remove services so that unavailable services are no longer offered.

---

## Bookings

- As a business owner, I want to create bookings on behalf of customers so that walk-in and phone bookings can be recorded.
- As a business owner, I want to approve or reject booking requests so that my schedule remains manageable.
- As a business owner, I want to reschedule appointments so that changes can be accommodated.
- As a business owner, I want to cancel appointments when necessary so that my calendar remains accurate.

---

## Reports

- As a business owner, I want to view business reports so that I can make informed decisions.
- As a business owner, I want to monitor revenue trends so that I can evaluate business performance.
- As a business owner, I want to identify popular services so that I can improve my offerings.

---

# Employee

## Daily Work

- As an employee, I want to log into FlowDesk so that I can access my schedule.
- As an employee, I want to view today's appointments so that I know my daily workload.
- As an employee, I want to update appointment statuses so that customers and managers remain informed.
- As an employee, I want to access customer notes so that I can provide personalised service.

---

## Customer Interaction

- As an employee, I want to search for customers so that I can quickly retrieve their information.
- As an employee, I want to view service details so that I know exactly what is required for each appointment.

---

# Customer

## Account

- As a customer, I want to create an account so that I can manage my bookings.
- As a customer, I want to log into my account so that I can access my booking history.
- As a customer, I want to update my personal information so that my account remains accurate.

---

## Booking

- As a customer, I want to browse available services so that I can choose the service I need.
- As a customer, I want to view available time slots so that I can book a convenient appointment.
- As a customer, I want to select my preferred employee so that I can book with someone I know.
- As a customer, I want to receive booking confirmation so that I know my appointment has been scheduled.
- As a customer, I want to receive appointment reminders so that I don't forget my booking.
- As a customer, I want to reschedule appointments so that I have flexibility if my plans change.
- As a customer, I want to cancel appointments so that unavailable time slots can be released.

---

## Profile

- As a customer, I want to view my booking history so that I can keep track of previous appointments.
- As a customer, I want to update my profile so that my contact information remains current.

---

# Platform Administrator

## Platform Management

- As a platform administrator, I want to view all registered businesses so that I can manage the platform.
- As a platform administrator, I want to approve or suspend business accounts so that platform policies are maintained.
- As a platform administrator, I want to monitor platform usage so that I understand system growth.

---

## Support

- As a platform administrator, I want to respond to support requests so that users receive assistance.
- As a platform administrator, I want to monitor system health so that platform reliability is maintained.

---

# Future User Stories

These user stories are planned for future releases.

## AI Business Assistant

- As a business owner, I want AI-generated business insights so that I can make smarter business decisions.
- As a business owner, I want recommendations for improving customer retention so that I can increase repeat business.

---

## Payments

- As a customer, I want to pay online so that I can complete my booking immediately.
- As a business owner, I want to track online payments so that I can monitor revenue.

---

## Website Generator

- As a business owner, I want to generate a business website automatically so that customers can discover my services online.

---

## Mobile Application

- As a business owner, I want to manage my business from my mobile phone so that I can stay connected while away from my desk.
